Passwd
Isi password kita

Pacman -S grub os-prober networkmanager wireless_tools ntfs-3g wpa_supplicant mtools dosfstools cups reflector xdg-utils xdg-user-dirs iwd network-mamager-applet nm-connection-editor 

grub-install /dev/sdaxxx
grub-install --target=i386-pc --force /dev/sdxxx

grub-mkconfig -o /boot/grub/grub.cfg

Warning: os-prober will not be executed to detect other bootable partitions then edit /etc/default/grub and add/uncomment:

GRUB_DISABLE_OS_PROBER=false


Systemctl enable NetworkManager
Systemctl enable org.cups.cupsd

Pacman -S sudo

useradd -m Ryan
Passwd Ryan
Isi pw nya

usermod -aG wheel,audio,video,storage Ryan

EDITOR=micro visudo
Uncomment wheel all all all

Exit chroot
Reboot

